text:
Hi team, i am using the personalization_token in my custom module to sends the latest products inventory emails according to users enquiry.  I wanted to get the products based on the make(personalization_token) but i am unable to fetch the products based on this personalization_token also i have enable programmable emails
```&lt;div&gt;
  &lt;h2&gt;Latest {{ table_label }} Products&lt;/h2&gt;
  {% set contact_make = personalization_token('contact.make_wits_test', '') %}

  contact_make:{{ contact_make}}

    {% if contact_make %}
      {% set contact_makeLower = contact_make.toLowerCase() %}

      {% set objects = crm_objects("Product", "make=" ~ contact_make ~ "&amp;limit=100&amp;order=-createdate", "make, hs_images, hs_sku, model, city, condition, dealer, exterior_color, zip, year, state, name, hs_updated_by_user_id, additional_image_url, createdate, price, id, hs_url") %}
                objects:{{objects}}
      {% if objects.results %}
        &lt;div style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;
          &lt;table style="width: 100%; text-align: center;"&gt;
            {% set objects.results = objects.results | reverse %}
            {% set filtered_rows = objects.results | slice(0, 8) %}

            {% for row in filtered_rows %}
              &lt;tr&gt;
                &lt;td style="background-color: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); margin: 2px; width: 48%; vertical-align: top; display: inline-block;"&gt;
                  {% if row.hs_images %}
                    &lt;img src="{{ row.hs_images }}" alt="{{ row.model }} of {{ row.make }}" style="width: 100%; height: auto;"&gt;
                  {% else %}
                    &lt;span style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; height: 200px; background-color: #ddd; text-align: center; line-height: 200px; color: #555;"&gt;No image available&lt;/span&gt;
                  {% endif %}

                  &lt;div style="padding: 16px;"&gt;
                    &lt;h3 style="margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 1.25em; color: #333;"&gt;{{ row.make }} {{ row.model }}&lt;/h3&gt;
                    &lt;p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1em; color: #555;"&gt;{{ row.price }}&lt;/p&gt;
                  &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;/td&gt;

                {% if loop.index % 2 == 1 %}
                  &lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;
                {% endif %}
              &lt;/tr&gt;
            {% endfor %}
          &lt;/table&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;

      {% else %}
        &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;No {{ table_label }} products found for {{ contact.email }}&lt;/p&gt;
      {% endif %}
    {% endif %}
&lt;/div&gt;```
